<li id="cite_note-Leventry2005-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Leventry2005_49-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFLeventry2005" class="citation web cs1">Leventry, Ellen (May 2005). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.beliefnet.com/story/166/story_16633_2.html">"Born-Again 'Battlestar'<span class="cs1-kern-right"></span>"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Beliefnet" title="Beliefnet">Beliefnet</a>. p.&#160;2.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Born-Again+%27Battlestar%27&amp;rft.pages=2&amp;rft.pub=Beliefnet&amp;rft.date=2005-05&amp;rft.aulast=Leventry&amp;rft.aufirst=Ellen&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beliefnet.com%2Fstory%2F166%2Fstory_16633_2.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKolob" class="Z3988"></span></span>
