<li id="cite_note-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-50">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">In 1979, Larson received an award from the Associated Latter-day Media Artists. "LDS Scene", <i><a href="/wiki/Ensign_(LDS_magazine)" title="Ensign (LDS magazine)">Ensign</a></i>, August 1979, 80.</span>
